title: YUS - Talisman (2014)
description:
Artist:  YUS
Album:   Talisman
Format:  MP3
Bitrate: 320kbps


Talisman is the second album from YUS, the sound of Phoenix-based artist Youceff Yunque Kabal, out on Manneken Records. It was created between Winter 2010/2011 and Spring 2014 at home, and mastered by Dietrich Schoenemann in NY. It features previous singles "Nowadays" and "20 Million", and showcases Kabal's disparate songwriting and production style.
